  autocmd!
  " BUG: must load extraTodo syntax from here again, because loading Syntastic
  " will clear the extraTodo syn group
  autocmd BufWritePre *
        \  call plug#load(syntax_checker) | call ExtraTodoHi()
        \| autocmd! plug_on_bufwritepre
augroup END

