" add some extra keywords to Todo highlight group
fu! ExtraTodoHi()
  syn keyword extraTodo HACK INFO BUG NOTE containedin=.*Comment.*
  hi def link extraTodo Todo
endfu
augroup extraTodoHi
  au!
  au BufEnter * call ExtraTodoHi() | autocmd! extraTodoHi
augroup END

