noremap <silent> <leader>x :Upq<CR>
vnoremap <silent> <leader>x <Esc>:Upq<CR>

" quit/force-quit to <leader>q/Q
noremap <silent> <leader>q :q<CR>
vnoremap <silent> <leader>q <Esc>:q<CR>
noremap <silent> <leader>Q :q!<CR>
vnoremap <silent> <leader>Q <Esc>:q!<CR>

